Hardware Components

ESP8266 (D1 Mini or NodeMCU)

Pins used:

D1 (GPIO5) → RDM6300_1_RX_PIN (RFID IN)

D2 (GPIO4) → RDM6300_2_RX_PIN (RFID OUT)

D5 (GPIO14) → IR sensor

D6 (GPIO12) → Relay Down

D7 (GPIO13) → Relay Up

D8 (GPIO15) → Relay Stop

A0 → Buzzer

RDM6300 RFID readers

Reader 1 → Entry

Reader 2 → Exit

Relays (3x)

Control motor to open/close shutter

Up, Down, Stop

IR Sensor

Detect vehicle presence

Buzzer

Feedback on card detection

Web/OTA

AsyncElegantOTA for OTA updates

WebSerial for logging

HTTP POST to log access in database